  m_Name: NeighborJournal_10
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalData
  id: 27
  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD h\xE0ng x\xF3m #10 \u2014 Th\u1EE3 s\u1EEDa xe t\xEAn Jack"
  category: 3
  content: "Chuy\u1EBFn xe bu\xFDt cu\u1ED1i c\xF9ng r\u1EDDi th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1 l\xFAc
    5 gi\u1EDD s\xE1ng. T\xF4i kh\xF4ng k\u1ECBp. Xe c\u1EE7a t\xF4i h\u1ECFng m\xE1y
    t\u1EEB tu\u1EA7n tr\u01B0\u1EDBc, kh\xF4ng c\xF3 ph\u1EE5 t\xF9ng. \u0110\u1EE9a
    h\xE0ng x\xF3m l\xE1i chi\u1EBFc Toyota \u0111i \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c n\u1EEDa
    \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng th\xEC b\u1ECB ch\u1EB7n \u1EDF tr\u1EA1m ki\u1EC3m d\u1ECBch.
    Nghe n\xF3i qu\xE2n \u0111\u1ED9i n\u1ED5 s\xFAng v\xE0o b\u1EA5t c\u1EE9 ai
    c\u1ED1 v\u01B0\u1EE3t r\xE0o. T\xF4i \u1EDF l\u1EA1i, trong x\u01B0\u1EDFng
    n\xE0y. C\xF3 \u0111\u1ED3 \u0103n v\xE0 n\u01B0\u1EDBc cho v\xE0i ng\xE0y."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
